609
00:44:24,780 --> 00:44:28,210
♪You demand dust
to stir up raging waves♪

610
00:44:28,320 --> 00:44:31,820
♪Souls will rise again♪

611
00:44:31,820 --> 00:44:35,170
♪You demand that fate
turn generous from now on♪

612
00:44:35,300 --> 00:44:38,720
♪To return everything
it once took from you♪

613
00:44:38,720 --> 00:44:41,360
♪You demand tomorrow♪

614
00:44:41,360 --> 00:44:44,400
♪To bloom beyond the ruins♪

615
00:44:44,400 --> 00:44:46,090
♪The light will come♪

616
00:44:58,440 --> 00:45:02,200
♪Who keeps warmth alive♪

617
00:45:02,400 --> 00:45:05,270
♪And beholds
flowers bloom in the abyss?♪

618
00:45:05,440 --> 00:45:09,140
♪Who never stops calling out♪

619
00:45:09,140 --> 00:45:12,530
♪And finally opens their eyes♪

620
00:45:12,640 --> 00:45:15,590
♪From a long slumber?♪

621
00:45:15,700 --> 00:45:17,040
♪The light will come♪

622
00:45:17,040 --> 00:45:20,340
♪You demand to pass through
life's perils in peace♪

